{"_path":"/maps/_ai/agents/a2a","_dir":"agents","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"A2A Protocol","description":"Agent-to-Agent 协议，Google 推出的多智能体协同开放标准","original_path":"_ai/agents/a2a.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"概述"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"概述"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A2A（Agent-to-Agent）协议是 Google 于 2025 年 4 月发布的开放标准，旨在解决不同 AI 智能体之间的互操作性问题，允许不同供应商、框架和平台的智能体跨系统安全协作，打破\"信息孤岛\"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://developers.google.com/agent-to-agent","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Google A2A 官方文档"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/google/A2A","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A2A 协议规范"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"核心设计原则"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"核心设计原则"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"能力发现capability-discovery"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"能力发现（Capability Discovery）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Agent 可动态发现其他 Agent 的能力，无需预先硬编码集成逻辑。通过标准化的能力描述格式，Agent 能理解其他 Agent 可以执行什么任务。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"任务管理task-management"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"任务管理（Task Management）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"支持多 Agent 协作完成复杂任务，包含任务创建、状态跟踪、结果返回的全生命周期管理。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"多模态通信multimodal-communication"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多模态通信（Multimodal Communication）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"支持文本、图像、音频、视频等多种数据格式的交换，适应不同场景需求。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"用户体验协商user-experience-negotiation"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"用户体验协商（User Experience Negotiati